high_descs: Turn right and face the table.
Grab the coffee cup out of the coffee maker.
Turn right and head toward the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the coffee cup in the fridge, close the door, wait a bit, open the fridge, and take the coffee cup out.
Turn around and head towards the table.
Place the coffee cup in the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put the coffee cup in the fridge for a bit.

high_descs: Turn to the right and walk to the table.
Pick up the coffee cup from the upper left corner of the table.
Turn around and walk across the room to the fridge.
Put the cup inside the fridge, close the door and wait for three seconds, then open the fridge and take the cup.
Turn around and walk across the room.
Place the cup on the table underneath the coffee machine.
Go to the coffee maker next to the toaster.
Take the cup in the coffee maker.
Turn and walk over to the refrigerator.
Chill the coffee cup in the refrigerator.
Take the chilled up to the coffee maker by the toaster.
Put the chilled coffee cup in the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold coffee cup in the coffee maker.
